text: Tai'an () is a prefecture-level city in western Shandong Province, China. In 2020, 5,472,217 people lived there. == Administration == Tai'an administers two districts, two county-level cities and two counties: * Taishan District () * Daiyue District () * Xintai City () * Feicheng City () * Ningyang County () * Dongping County () Category:Cities in China Category:Shandong
title: Tai'an
